{"tid":2146952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：會嚴肅處理不專業教師　若非常過分或取消註冊","createTime":"2020-08-09T02:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T07:02:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9526655641953d87c9dc3f9fe1d572723031a0aa","tid":2146952,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:30:57.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄說，局方會為教師提供更多培訓，讓教師多些理解身份認同的問題，以及維護國家安全的責任。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄出席一個電台節目時說，絕大部分教師都是專業地教導學生理性分析事物，但對於一些不專業的教師，當局會抽出來嚴肅處理，如果情況非常過分，會考慮取消有關人士的教師註冊，局方現時正在處理幾個較嚴重的個案，但會給予足夠時間讓有關教師解釋。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，不會低估學校推行國家安全教育的難度，希望學界及社會明白政府的決心，當局會推廣多些關於國家安全的教材，並與學校商討制定推行國安教育的詳細指引。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542669-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542669-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=4aec65f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542669-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=df188be0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542669-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9e03b4742bba90993678977d50d92ebf230cb3a0","tid":2146952,"uid":160373,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣好快入制裁名單"},{"pid":"9530b903ed6ff190fe0b0aabb0839518fefba52f","tid":2146952,"uid":7323,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街d仔女就外國讀書，香港人仔女老師就俾呢個仆街搞。"},{"pid":"2ac2bd756f7b2a7302a77f556120e21ec1c3eac7","tid":2146952,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6018e432075103f78a72c94b72d2