br />\n<br />\n等於英國當年都無強逼人認同香港係英國, 否則, 工賊會就死咗好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:40:54.000Z","msg":"淘寶全國免運冇份<br />\n所以香港不是中國的一部份"},{"pid":"1127db43b1588ac077b1011758cc724763b2973c","tid":2146952,"uid":155371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"呢個真係仆街黎"},{"pid":"c77a131640b86a77da88b6aa47c2ec117629c804","tid":2146952,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:27:37.000Z","msg":"不要低估香港人反共及外國滅共的決心"},{"pid":"76ab60fbd161ebaab96993bc26d94b5413803fb1","tid":2146952,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"其實有好多教師覺得佢係好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b836bbefb1c47e034edfbce18a421a697d8c5fc","tid":2146952,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ab60fbd161ebaab96993bc26d94b5413803fb1","tid":2146952,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"其實有好多教師覺得佢係好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"因為上一任唔得掂太柒"},{"pid":"cb1c25be3316276aa57fc19cdcef6755bdeb6355","tid":2146952,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦 知你好想入制裁list啦<br />\n要加大力度同五眼聯盟爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72df12bc58924364bff7e29f8e317048b4a75901","tid":2146952,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"玩鬥快制裁？"},{"pid":"cc0d1966f1aba46850e5a303acd9d1408c431696","tid":2146952,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"消滅奶共狗<br />\n天經地義"},{"pid":"c31c141a98d9ddfd5d8c2e884f84e6389a335088","tid":2146952,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0